Module scrabble.main
Package cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types

Class ScrInt

java.lang.Object
cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types.ScrInt
All Implemented Interfaces:
IOperations
public class ScrInt
extends java.lang.Object
implements IOperations
The ScrInt class wraps an int in an object. A ScrInt object contains a single field whose type is int
